{
  "stem": "942.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was in this particular business with my uncle.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my father had a small distillery.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had a place called The Cellar.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was actually a cellar where you had to go down about 15 or so steps underground.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was sort of like a pub, but he was only serving like hard spirits where the farmers used to come to drink.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we also used to make some liqueurs that he was selling in bottles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I recollect filling bottles with different liqueurs-- chocolate liqueurs, creme de menthe, or pear liqueur, and putting on all these fancy labels, you know, from different parts of the world, and putting the red wax on the bottles to close the cork type of thing, and then put them in a straw and jacket.",
      "word_count": 55
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember I used to deliver these to different customers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I remember, my father had many of his friends come there, fellows his age.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "At that age, when I was five, six, seven, I thought that my father was a very old man.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I realize that he was only in his early 30s, actually.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so in this town, we lived with our neighbors who were Christians, Gentiles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know, Jews did not live all together in one area.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We were sort of dispersed in between.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Most of the Jewish people were-- they had small businesses-- textile, yard goods, and, groceries, stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We were very Orthodox Jews, like most everybody in this town.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "All of the Jews were Orthodox Jews.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we went to synagogue on a regular basis.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And especially on Shabbat, you know, Friday evening, we all went to synagogue with my grandfather, my father, and my uncle.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And of course, Saturday morning again, we did that.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
